direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Who's the girl?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: It's started again. You're already jealous. You are going to do the same thing you did during the war...you're going to sabotage this.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I'm insulted frankly.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Don't you play that game. You are being facetious.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: No, I'm being serious. You care about the girl, it's obvious. Not in a friendship or I'm curious about human behavior way. Quinn sits down beside him.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: So why are you here?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Have you told her?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Who I am? Of course not!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn you only have a few days left and you care for this girl- (beat) - What's the harm in telling her?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: There's a lot of harm in telling her.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: If this is real and you really care for this girl, you have to tell her. It's only fair to her.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: She has a best friend who is very guarded of me...It's odd she eluded to the same thing. You know the whole "I'm hiding something, and I need to come out into the open" thing.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Sounds to me like she is right. Quinn gets up and walks to the door.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Well I better do this now then.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yeah you don't want to lose your nerve.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Can you let yourself out?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Of course. Quinn slowly opens the door and walks out. The door creeps shut behind him. Louis smiles to himself, feeling satisfaction. His face looks evil, almost demonic. EXT. ZOEY'S APARTMENT BUILDING- SOMETIME LATER In almost a "romantic movie" way, Quinn runs toward Zoey's apartment. When he reaches the door he knocks like his life depends on it. Anna swings the door open, she's obviously surprised to see Quinn.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What the hell? You can hear Jack inside the apartment.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What the fuck?!? I want to watch Bring me the Head of Alfredo Garcia in peace!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I need to see Zoey.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What about tomorrow? Or never is good. You hear Zoey off screen.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What's going on?? Zoey comes to the doorway and stands behind Anna.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn? What's wrong?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I need to talk to you, it's important. Quinn grabs her by the arm and pulls her outside, pushing her right past Anna.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Jesus Christ! Anna slams the door shut, leaving Zoey and Quinn outside.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I need to tell you everything. Anna is so right.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What are you talking about? Anna is right?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I've not been honest with you about what I do...or who I am.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I need to come clean. I want you to trust me. I want your friends to trust me.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (nervous laugh)
direction.name: direction

dialogue.raw_text: : TITLE CARD: 3 DAYS LEFT EXT. OPEN FIELD-DAY Quinn is sitting cross legged in the middle of the field. He seems as though he is in the middle of a trance.
dialogue.name: dialogue

direction.raw_text: Quinn, just spit it out.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (beat) I'm an archangel named Moroni and I basically represent "light" or everything that's good. Louis, my friend, represents "darkness". Every seventy years we have to fight to the death. If I win everything stays the way it is. The world continues turning. If I lose, Louis takes on the role of the Antichrist and the apocalypse will be unleashed. I'm talking Book of Revelations stuff here. So I only have a limited time left in this world... (beat) I want to spend that time with you. Zoey is stunned, silent.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Oh honey... Zoey touches his face.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You must have a brain tumor or something. You're obviously mentally ill.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Zoey? I...
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . Zoey puts her finger up to his lips to quiet him.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Shhh. You need me more than ever. Zoey reaches down and takes a confused Quinn's hand. She leads him to the door. Like a sheep herder, she takes Quinn inside of the apartment. The last image we see is the apartment door slamming behind them.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: : DARKNESS FLASHBACK-ZOEY'S HOME-YEARS EARLIER-DAY Zoey, roughly 2 years old, sits in the floor of her parent's home playing. Her DAD, only seen from the waist down, walks in front of Zoey with his bible in hand. He makes it to Zoey's MOM, on the other side of the room
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You're not even helping me!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I don't even know what you want!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I can't run my congregation with this sickness!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: The sickness is in your head.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You're too busy running around doing whatever you feel like. I'm going to fall apart and it's all on you. FLASHBACK-ZOEY'S HOME-TEN YEARS LATER-DAY Zoey, now 12, is going through some boxes in the closet. Her head bumps a shelf and a box falls on her. When she goes to pick up the box she finds a ton of VHS tapes.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . She goes through the box looking at the labels: "Anna age 7" "Anna age 10" "Anna age 12". FLASHBACK-ZOEY'S ROOM-A FEW MOMENTS LATER The glow of Zoey's TV fills her face. We can neither see nor hear what she is watching. Zoey looks like she is about to throw up.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Last night?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yes?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Did you?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Enjoy myself? Of course.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Based on how you are acting this morning I have my doubts. That's not what I meant though. You woke up screaming.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: It was nothing.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I understand if you don't want to talk about it. I'm just concerned.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: It's not a big deal. It was...a...well wouldn't call it a nightmare...repressed memory. Hell, it's not repressed...I think of it all the time.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What is it?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You don't want to hear about it. Quinn touches her hand.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Please? Zoey takes a deep breath.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: My father, I mentioned him before, was a Baptist minister. He always said he had this "sickness". He begged my mom for help, it was more important though for her to having shopping and dinner dates with her girlfriends. Anna, my friend that "loves you", has been in my life since I was tiny. She used to come over all the time. My Dad adored her. When I was around twelve I found something in the closet...tapes. My Dad and Anna from the time she was like seven...He... (starts tearing up) I showed my Mom, and Dad...well he got out of prison when I was seventeen. I don't see him anymore. His church, even though they knew he had a problem disowned him. He wouldn't have done that to Anna if my mom would have supported him, got him help.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Who do you think is to blame?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He tried to get help Quinn, he reached out to my Mom. I should have protected Anna too...I mean-
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: -None of this was your fault.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I have to protect people. This was out of my control, you Quinn...What's going on with you...I have control of that. Quinn looks at Zoey. He loves her, but a part of him pities her too. EXT. PARK-RIVERSIDE-LATER Zoey is curled up under Quinn's arm as they sit on the same bench from earlier. Quinn stares out toward the river. It's obvious he is pondering over his choices.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I love being with you.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Me too.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I can't renege on my responsibilities with Louis though. Zoey sits up.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You're not actually going to fight your friend to the death are you?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I know you don't understand this. We just need to make the most of our time.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn, in 2 days things are going to be normal. This is just a delusion.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I know you don't understand. I just need to go see Louis today.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I understand that. Quinn leans his head back. He catches something out of the corner of his eye. QUINN'S POV Quinn sees Ryan Blood hiding behind a tree. He is taking video of Quinn and Zoey with a "smart phone". PARK-RIVERSIDE Quinn jolts up. Zoey is alarmed.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What is it? Quinn doesn't answer. He gets up and runs to the... TREE Quinn looks behind the tree, but Ryan is long gone. Zoey comes up from behind, she places her hand on Quinn's shoulder.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What was wrong?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: My neighbor Ryan Blood...looks like he's spying on me.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What are you talking about?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I need to go see Louis. INT. RYAN BLOOD'S APARTMENT-LATER Louis is watching the video on the smart phone. He's seen enough, he throws it back to Ryan. Louis tosses trash off the couch so he can sit down.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (sitting down) I thought him admitting his true self would break them up-
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . Ryan plops down in his computer desk chair.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: -Instead he is still hot and heavy with her. (beat) He even did the "bipty boom" last night.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: The fight is pointless.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: It's not pointless. The game has just changed is all. (beat) We have two levels here: one is making sure we keep him engaged. (beat) Honestly though that's an afterthought at this point-
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: So what's the next move? Ryan reaches into his desk drawer.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (still searching) Well when he does become engaged... Ryan throws something at Louis. LOUIS POV Louis catches the item. He looks down to see a nine millimeter.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: ...We need to make sure you still have the advantage. INT. ZOEY AND ANNA'S APARTMENT-LATER Zoey is pacing back and forth. Jack rubs his face in frustration. He is tired of watching Zoey tear herself up over this guy. Anna tries to step into Zoey's path attempting to get her attention
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What are you doing?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . Zoey is jittery, she can't handle Anna blocking her way.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I haven't heard from Quinn since he wigged out today.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Well honestly maybe that's a good thing.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He needs me.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He doesn't need you! Not everyone needs you!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (frustrated) This isn't about me and you-
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: -This is about me and you! You think you can make up for what happened. The fact you didn't notice, couldn't save me in time. You were a child! I was a child! You couldn't have saved your father either! Your mother couldn't have, no one could have! He was a fucking pedophile! Zoey slaps Anna across the face.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Hate me all you want, but it's impossible to redeem yourself for things you had no control over. Jack is sick and tired of this display.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Just show her the fucking file. Jack gets up.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (confused) What fucking file? EXT. LOUIS APARTMENT-CONTINUOUS Quinn runs toward Louis' apartment. His KNOCKS sound like a jackhammer on the door. Louis answers.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: We have a problem.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You're right. We do. Louis moves slightly and we see Ryan Blood in the background. Louis slowly closes the door in a stunned Quinn's face. INT. LOUIS APARTMENT Louis turns toward Ryan.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I thought coming here would give us some privacy from Quinn.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I think it worked out perfectly. INT. ZOEY'S APARTMENT BUILDING-CONTINUOUS Jack walks into the room holding a file folder. Zoey is sitting on the couch trying to get a grip. Jack throws the file in her lap.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: So is the file folder for dramatic effect?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: No it was to keep everything organized... (beat) ...and for dramatic effect. Suddenly Zoey's cell phon rings. She sets the folder aside and answers.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn? INTERCUT EXT. STREET CORNER Quinn is on a pay phone, he's shaking. At this point he is lost on what his next move should be.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Ryan Blood!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You mentioned that earlier. What is going on?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: He's with Louis. They're planning to kill me.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I thought that was the whole plan.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: No it's...this isn't like Louis. I think he is trying to cheat his way to a win.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Why don't you come over here.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I can't!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Come on Quinn get a grip. Just calm down and come over here.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You're right.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: so just come on over and we'll talk.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: No I mean you're right. I need to get control of myself. I have a destiny. I need to figure out my next move.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn? No wait- Quinn hangs up the phone. ZOEY AND ANNA'S APARTMENT Zoey slowly drops her cell phone to the floor. Jack picks up the folder Zoey set aside.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What is it?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I don't know. He's losing it. Jack hands her the folder.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You need to look at this. Zoey takes the folder from him and starts reading.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I spent a lot of time gathering that information.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: So what is all this?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn Wilson and Louis Marks were orphans. Zoey is flipping through documents.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn displayed some erratic behavior from the beginning. One of the staff members was Mormon and they would read stories to Quinn out of the Book Of Mormon. That employee was later fired, but a seed was planted in Quinn's head. He kept going on about how he and Louis were meant to fight to the death. Some of the children at the time claim Louis would encourage this behavior. He probably thought this was Quinn's attempt at playing. (beat) As things continued the staff at the orphanage thought Quinn needed help beyond what they could offer. They sent Quinn to a hospital. Zoey puts the folder down, the documents fall to the floor.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You're not telling me anything I didn't already know.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: That makes it worse. You're going to continue this now that you know for a fact that he is nuts?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I'm too far into this now. I don't have a choice. Zoey picks the documents up and places them in the folder. She then tosses the folder on the coffee table.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Why don't you let us save you? Please Zoey.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Let me be guys. Zoey walks to her bedroom, leaving Anna and Jack exhausted. ZOEY AND ANNA'S APARTMENT-EARLY MORNING The apartment is quiet. Anna no where in sight, more than likely in her room sleeping. Jack is passed out on the couch. Zoey walks in, it's obvious she hasn't slept all night. She scoots Jack's legs over and sits on the couch. She proceeds to pick up the file folder. She starts thumbing through the documents. After a few moments she finds one of interest. She reaches over and pushes Jack.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (rousing up) Ehhh...what? You better be a hot bear of a man. Jack looks up and sees Zoey.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Or Zoey...What do you need hun? Zoey hands Jack a document from the folder.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What's this? Jack's eyes try to focus on the document.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Looks like a room list from the psych hospital.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I gathered that. Under Quinn's room...
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn and his roommate is listed.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Quinn's roommate was Ryan Blood?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yeah...looks that way.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Ah fuck.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: We need to talk. Louis turns around to face Ryan.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: About?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Strategy.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Strategy?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yes. I have a method-
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: have to hear this.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: point system-
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (confused) - Like 12 steps?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Exactly. It's a sure fire plan to throw Quinn off of his game Louis laughs.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Oh I am so all ears.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Well the first thing you need is a battle cry.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Excuse me? A battle cry?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yes a battle cry. Every great warrior has one.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: And a battle cry is going to give me the advantage in battle?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Of course it will. Why don't you try one out?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yeah, try one out right now. It's liberating.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I'd rather not.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Come on.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (extremely confused) Right here?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Here I'll go first- Ryan let's out a scream that sounds as though he is being sodomized.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: That was...interesting.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: See? (beat) Your turn. Louis looks around.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: So right now?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Of course. Louis inhales deeply and then lets out a scream. It comes out more like frightened little girl.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Oh come on! That sounds like you are scared of the battle. What? Are you scared of Quinn? You probably are- Louis lets out another scream, this one is slightly better.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: That's good! Come on! Louis lets out another one that actually causes Ryan to jump back.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Yes that's what I'm talking about! Out of nowhere, Quinn walks up to the two of them.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (noticing Quinn) Quinn?!? Good to see you! Quinn grabs Louis' arm.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: We need to talk.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (to Ryan) Excuse me for a second. Louis walks with Quinn to a spot that gives them some distance away from Ryan.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I know that guy and I don't trust him.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I don't trust you anymore.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Your new friend is dangerous.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: So is yours.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Leave her out of this.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You fighting tomorrow morning Quinn?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: It's over. This whole thing is nuts. I'm walking away.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Let me walk away from you first then. Louis starts to walk away from Quinn. He turns around as he continues to walk backwards.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I'm coming at you! You are in this game like it or not! EXT. ORPHANAGE-DAY Zoey's car pulls up in front of an historic brick building. She slowly gets out and starts to look the structure over. It's almost like she is trying to assess if she has the right place. INT. ORPHANAGE-CONTINUOUS A awkward young man, JAKE, is sorting through boxes. He's kneeled on the floor organizing a mess of files. Zoey walks up and tries to attract his attention.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Excuse me? Jake comes out of his world of file sorting. He looks up at Zoey.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) Yes.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: . Jake stands.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I'm looking for Mrs. Rhodes. I believe the people here referred to her as "mother".
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) People look for a lot of things. Zoey is confused.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: I'm sure they do. (looking at the boxes) You guys shutting down?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) We are ceasing operations.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Is there something wrong with you? MRS. RHODES, a 60 year old odd looking lady, comes out of the back.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Calm down. You need to calm down and count to ten.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What? I don't know what that means. Mrs. Rhodes starts waving her hands at Zoey. She flaps them up and down in her face.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You have to calm down and meditate.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Um...no...listen do you know Quinn Wilson and Louis Marks? They grew up here. Mrs. Rhodes steps back like a vampire who has just seen a cross.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: No...You need to leave!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: And give me your shirt.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Um...no. Zoey turns around and starts to leave. Mrs. Rhodes starts screaming at the top of her lungs.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You better make your peace with God girl! The end is coming, those boys are ushering in a new era! Zoey runs down the hallway toward the front door. EXT. ORPHANAGE Zoey runs outside and makes it to her car. She hits the roof of her vehicle in anger
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What a fucking nut house!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) Excuse me! Zoey jumps up and screams. She sees Jake standing creepily behind her.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: What!
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) I know the young boys you speak of.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (doesn't care) And?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) I was here when Quinn got sent to the mental hospital. It was like the other one set it up.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Wait Louis? You think Louis made Quinn appear crazy?
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) They both believed the same thing. Louis was just smart enough to hide it.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: There is more to it than that.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) I don't understand
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Listen "Robot Boy", where did this whole belief come from? This isn't something two kids come up with on their own.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) Yes I believe a seed was planted.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: Exactly. I heard there was an employee that got fired for sharing Mormon mythology with the boys.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: (monotone) No. Off base. He's not the right one. INTERCUT INT. ZOEY AND ANNA'S APARTMENT- A FEW MOMENTS LATER Jack sits at the PC while chatting away on his cell phone. It appears he is looking up information for who ever is on the other end. INT.ZOEY'S CAR- CONTINUOUS Zoey is parked in a parking lot, while she chats on her cell phone with Jack.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: You might be right sweetheart. The employee I was telling you about earlier was instrumental in getting Appleridge Orphanage shut down.
direction.name: direction

direction.raw_text: How?
direction.name: direction

INT.CAFE-LATER Quinn and Zoey are having coffee. It's obvious Zoey had a rough night. She takes a sip of coffee, her mind is distant.
